  <brief_title>Relief of Acute Bronchoconstriction/Asthma Using the Non-Invasive AlphaCore Device</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-Invasive Neurostimulation of the Vagus Nerve With the AlphaCore™ Device, for the Relief of Acute Bronchoconstriction Due to Asthma</official_title>
